Title: Parallel Internet Search Engine
Body: Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 01:25:50 GMT Server: Apache/1.1.1 Content-type: text/html Content-length: 1098 Last-modified: Tue, 05 Nov 1996 06:32:42 GMT Parallel Internet Search Engine Parallel Internet search engine The idea is to send your query to a server A first, then server A sends the query to Alta Vista, Lycos, Yahoo and Webcrawler at the same time.
